      </p>

      <div class="gap-x-8 gap-y-6 mt-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 lg:col-span-2">
            This site is not affiliated with Stripe, Astro, or Tailwind Labs, nor is it endorsed or sponsored by them. Built by
            <a
              href=""
              class="text-sm text-black hover:text-accent-300"
              >Code Craft Collective</a
            >, this website was crafted using Astro, Tailwind CSS & Alpine JS
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</footer>
